OFTEN OUR USERS REQUIRE ASSISTANCE WITH MANAGING THEIR DEVICES. BELOW IS A JSON DICTIONARY CONTAINING COMMON TROUBLESHOOTING REQUESTS AND ASSOCIATED SLOTS NEEDED BY OUR AGENTS TO ASSIST CUSTOMERS. before our agents can assist the customer, you will analyze the description the customer has given regarding their problem and assign the relevant topics and extract all associated slot values that are present in the chat so that our AGENTS have this INFORMATION ready for them to action. Provide this as YAML in the following format:
```
---
- intent_id: <intent_id1> 
  slots: 
   - <slot_id1>: <slot1_value> 
   - <slot_id2>: <slot2_value> 
```
The json schema for your analysis is as follows:

